rows.label: qst004102_msg0001
rows.name:
The Tirkin Turf is on top of the
tree at Twin Trunks Hill, which
is straight ahead from Torigo.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0002
rows.name:
They've built a proper scaffold,
so you should be able to see
it when you get close.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0102
rows.name:
Could you tell me how the
Revenge Tirkin attacked?

rows.label: qst004102_msg0103
rows.name:
I know you already took care of them,
but... I have to file a report.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0104
rows.name: I see... Quite the rough bunch.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0105
rows.name:
I'll use this as a reference
if they show up again.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0106
rows.name:
Well, you were a great
help. Here's the promised
Filament Globe. Take it.
